{"word":"ἐκκρεμάννυμι","slug":"ἐκκρεμάννυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκκρεμάννυμι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-κρεμάσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to hang from</i> or <i>upon</i> a thing; <el>τι ἔκ τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to hang on by, cling to</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to be devoted to</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><el>ἐκκρέμαμαι</el><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to hang from, depend upon</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}